response.overview: When Pete and Ellie decide to start a family, they stumble into the world of foster care adoption. They hope to take in one small child but when they meet three siblings, including a rebellious 15 year old girl, they find themselves speeding from zero to three kids overnight.
response.tagline: Just add chaos, laughter, awkwardness, mistakes, love...
response.title: Instant Family
